ObjectStates.Name: Checker_red
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
----#include components/button
----#include !/dominion/setup
function setup()
  for _,card in pairs(SUPPLY_CARDS) do
    obj = getObjectFromGUID(card.guid)
    card:setup(obj)
  end
end

----#include !/dominion/setup

function onLoad()
  params = {
      click_function = "setup",
      function_owner = self,
      label          = "",
      position       = {0, 0.3, 0},
      rotation       = {0, 0, 0},
      width          = 600,
      height         = 600,
      font_size      = 340,
      color          = {0,0,0,0},
      font_color     = {1, 1, 1},
      tooltip        = "Set up a new game of Dominion.",
  }
  self.createButton(params)
end
